                <p>People have short attention spans. When viewing web pages, there are no exceptions to this rule. Unfortunately when verifying a new user account, Dwolla was repeatedly encountering a problem – verification speeds that ranged from super fast to dead slow, depending on the bank. In order to keep the user engaged, we needed a way to entertain and show progress at the same time. This SVG animation does just the trick.  Built to be light-weight and responsive using vector graphics, this little slice of cool gives the waiting user something to gawk at.</p>
